            "key": "volunteer_01",
            "body_en": "Would you like to help us bring Neighbor Express to your community? [Sign your city up here][1]. \n\nIf Neighbor Express is already live in your community, the best way to help is to volunteer directly with them at their Neighbor Express website. On top of deliveries, they may appreciate volunteers willing to spread the word. \n\nWe'd love your help to spread the word, too, to anyone you know in local government or community groups taking care of residents at high-risk of COVID-19.\n\n  [1]: https://landing-page-gamma.now.sh/bring_to_my_city\n",
