            "body_en": "We are a team of volunteers, government servants, educators, and nonprofits and our strength comes from tapping into existing public-private-nonprofit networks in communities and willingness to collaborate. \n\nThrough the support of generous donors like you, community partners are able to ensure that every person in your area in need receives help. A gift to your city helps fund meal deliveries, purchases of necessary supplies, and other support.\n\nTo donate, email neighborexpress@gmail.com.\n",
